stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE
    IDLE --> LOAD_Q : start
    LOAD_Q --> LOAD_K
    LOAD_K --> PRESCREEN
    PRESCREEN --> COMPUTE
    COMPUTE --> SOFTM
    SOFTM --> WRITEBACK
    WRITEBACK --> IDLE : done
    note right of PRESCREEN : prescreener latency = 2 cycles\nmask ready before data
    note right of COMPUTE : PE array valid_mask gates MACs
    note right of SOFTM : masked softmax (exp LUT + reciprocal)
